folder: 123rd Street & Mt. Morris Park West, Manhattan, NY
text:
3-5 West 123rd Street, west of, adjoining, and at the N.W. corner of Mt. Morris Avenue. Mt. Morris Avenue is a short avenue that extends from 120th to 124th Street, on the west side of Mt. Morris Park.

About 1913.
